README

SUMMARY
-------

The DataTransferKit is a package for parallel data transfer between arbitrary 
physics codes. Interfaces are provided for data access to each physics. See 
doxygen documentation for more developer details.


DEPENDENCIES
------------

The DataTransferKit has direct dependecies on the following Trilinos packages:

*: Teuchos
*: Tpetra


CONFIGURE and BUILD
-------------------

The DataTransferKit uses the TriBITS cmake build system. See doc/build_notes/ 
for a sample configure script and additional configure/build documentation.


TEST
----

ctest - Run package the unit tests when enabled.